						               													<description>F&amp;uacute;tbol Base is the board game with which you can experience football as a coach and a player at the same time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Choose the Football 11 or Football 8 board for your games and design the best formation against your opponent. &amp;#10;Improve your technique and aim on the practise field and enjoy your evolution as a player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With Football Base live all the passion of football without leaving home.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Place the players with the formation of your choice (4-3-3 / 5-3-2 / 4-4-2, etc.).&amp;#10;     Put the ball in play... &amp;#10;     The side in possession of the ball is the one closest to the ball. (or whoever the referee says so)&amp;#10;     A player can only have two consecutive touches of the ball. And the maximum number of touches of the ball per area is 4.&amp;#10;     Shooting at goal is allowed only in the shooting area&amp;#10;     When the player in possession prepares to pass or shoot, the defender can only move 1 player to try hinder her/him&amp;#10;     The player formation can only be altered when the game is stopped (ball out of play)&amp;#10;     If a player shoots and knocks down an opponent it is a foul; On a forward, a penalty is given.&amp;#10;     Shooting or passing is only valid if hit with your hand on the player.&amp;#10;     There can be three changes plus the goalkeeper. &amp;#10;     Games last 40 minutes. Plus extra time or penalty shootout if needed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
